{"type":"answer","id":99705,"parentType":"question","parentId":12860,"uid":16872,"contents":"哪個種族重要嗎，所謂漢人之間的分別分分鐘也比得上其他種族，重要的是你對哪個文化更有歸屬感，更有傳承和維護它的心，不要被血統論綁架，因為如果你追溯得夠長久，人類大致都是同一群祖先，甚至現代的不同物種都是同一群祖先，沒有甚麼真正不真正的種族，所有人都是<s>雜種</s>混血，或所有人都是遠親。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/w0RCQBZ.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/w0RCQBZ.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/w0RCQBZ.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/kWk3sCJ.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/kWk3sCJ.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/kWk3sCJ.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/4Ti4DHe.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/4Ti4DHe.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/4Ti4DHe.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2019-12-09","agreeCount":4,"discussionCount":0}